==English==
===Etymology===
: [[free]] + [[recycle]]

===Verb===
'''freecycle'''
# (US) The act of giving an item freely as a method of recycling, made popular by ''Freecycle America'', "The Freecycle Network", and other groups that grew out of the grassroots freecycling movement.

